Interface RendererInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
JSONRenderer, Renderer, TextRenderer
public interface RendererInterface

rencererInterface defines an interface for working with rendered identifiers . Can enter an object, printMetadata, and leave. These methods are meant to populate a class level variable in the Renderer
